metadata.name: Venice's Littlest Explorer #1/9
metadata.description:
"Venice's Littlest Explorer" showcases a dachshund pup exploring the beautiful and intricate alleyways of Venice. 
The artwork has a whimsical quality, with the pup discovering the city's wonders. 
The background features stunning and intricate architecture and the intricate colors and textures give the piece a truly baroque feel.
